WHAT IS IT?
-----------

  'DominoH' is a Workbench game in which you create 28 dominos
using the numbers displayed on the game board. Avoid forming more
than one domino that have the same pair of numbers. Complete the
game in the least amount of moves possible.

  Have fun!

FEATURES
--------

-Simple installation: just run the game and play!

-Small package, the Lha archive is smaller than 50K, so it
 doesn't take ages to download :)

-The game plays on the Workbench screen and its window is
 resizeable.

